fields.description: While [supportsNavigation|https://appcelerator.github.io/appc-docs/latest/#!/api/Titanium.App.iOS.SearchableItemAttributeSet-property-supportsNavigation] and [supportsPhoneCall|https://appcelerator.github.io/appc-docs/latest/#!/api/Titanium.App.iOS.SearchableItemAttributeSet-property-supportsPhoneCall] are there and talk about the related phoneNumbers, latitude and longitude properties these are in fact [missing|https://github.com/appcelerator/titanium_mobile/blob/master/iphone/Classes/TiAppiOSSearchableItemAttributeSetProxy.m], making the first 2 unusable.
fields.summary: Ti.App.iOS.SearchableItemAttributeSet is missing phoneNumbers, latitude and longitude
